OL,5, The mother of a girl murdered in 1992  
OL,6, says she is taking legal action against
OL,7, a police force over her 30-year wait   
OL,8, for justice.                           
OL,10,FNikki Allan, seven, was lured to a     
OL,11,Fderelict building in Sunderland where  
OL,12,Fshe was repeatedly beaten and stabbed. 
OL,14,FHer ex-neighbour David Boyd was jailed 
OL,15,Ffor her murder earlier in May. Nikki's 
OL,16,Fmum Sharon Henderson said Northumbria  
OL,17,FPolice should have caught him sooner.  
OL,19,FThe force told the BBC it would not    
OL,20,Fcomment over any legal action.         
